    "summaryBullets": [
      "Electric charges and fields are fundamental concepts in electromagnetism.",
      "Electric charges create electric fields, which exert forces on other charges.",
      "The spark or shock experienced when handling certain materials is due to the buildup and sudden discharge of static electricity."
    ],
    "whyImportant": "Coulomb's Law, Electric Field",
